title: tab重载报错
author: 表示路过
txt_content:
TAB插件 重载的时候会报错

[TAB] File plugins\TAB\errors.txt exists and is not empty. Please take a look at the errors and try to correct them. You can also join our discord for assistance. After you resolve them, delete the file

我看了他那个errors.txt里是这样的
